			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Well, I know it exsists, that's about all I know. The quest is in mistemoore and the sword is 1h slashing. 7dmg 21delay, magical. non-lore, no drop no trade. called Electrum Bladed wakushi, i'm not sure about that last part. more info would be helpful. thx
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
