		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Lord Grimrot is a level 30-40 SK in south karana...his level is determined by what form he is in. he is either skeleton, or human (in full plate).  the loot differs when you kill him depending on his form. In skele form he has a rusty scythe (give it to the paladin guildmaster in queynos) and sometimes a misshapen heart. in human form..he has a wicked lore no drop scythe...called the opal scythe. atk 15 dly 48 +10 sv poison and disease casts disease cloud..
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
